        "subject": "LUS-16915 osd-ldiskfs: use __vfs_getxattr in __osd_xattr_get",
        "message": "LUS-16915 osd-ldiskfs: use __vfs_getxattr in __osd_xattr_get\n\n__osd_xattr_get() fails to get security attibutes via vfs_getxattr:\nvfs_getxattr\n  xattr_getsecurity\n    security_inode_getsecurity\n      cap_inode_getsecurity\n        dentry = d_find_any_alias(inode)\n          if (!dentry)\n            return -EINVAL;\n\nbecasue ldiskfs’ inode has empty alias list.\n\nResort to __vfs_getxattr() in __osd_xattr_get().\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-12018\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <vladimir.saveliev@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I63a79f5bb39f10e2bfe1a66dcd91703d819dd193\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
